Swami Vishwananda: Uncovering a Dark Web of Manipulation, Fraud, and Exploitation

In this deep investigation, we uncover shocking allegations against Swami Vishwananda, including claims of sexual misconduct, financial manipulation, and cult-like practices. Followers allege they were pressured into donating large sums of money, while others claim attempts to silence dissent through cyber tactics and legal threats.

➡️ Watch to uncover:

Sexual Misconduct Claims: Disturbing accusations involving followers.
Financial Exploitation: How donations were coerced.
Cult-like Control: Allegations of isolating devotees from their families.

Full story: https://www.fraudadviser.com/swami-vishwananda/
